estion of remedies, and the truly difficult questions for me and my framewo=
rks.

The fact of the matter is that while antitrust is framed as correcting the =
market, it is in fact interfering with the market; that was one of the poin=
ts I was trying to raise in yesterday=E2=80=99s introduction. I think it=E2=
